Additional note: VizKit is an administration toolkit that can invoke
commands which change system state (e.g. disk optimization, firewall
settings, service management). It is provided for legitimate system
administration purposes. You are solely responsible for reviewing what a
command does (visible in the relevant Data\*.dat file) before running it,
and for any consequences of running it on a system you manage.
